00:37:44,000 --> 00:37:46,083
♪ What a beauty ♪

660
00:37:46,500 --> 00:37:48,916
♪ What a beauty ♪

661
00:37:48,958 --> 00:37:52,125
♪ In the voice of Padanna. ♪

662
00:37:54,458 --> 00:37:55,666
O' priest!

663
00:37:55,708 --> 00:37:57,416
O' Landlord!

664
00:37:57,916 --> 00:37:59,708
What do you think lies
ahead for all of you?

665
00:37:59,708 --> 00:38:01,333
Will it be the
poison or the elixir?

666
00:38:02,083 --> 00:38:03,791
If it's poisonous,
let God take care of it.

667
00:38:03,833 --> 00:38:05,458
If it's elixir,
let this village savour it.

668
00:38:05,500 --> 00:38:06,958
Let the procession begin.

669
00:38:07,500 --> 00:38:08,583
I'm elated!

670
00:38:08,583 --> 00:38:10,875
♪ What a beauty? ♪

