00:38:32,250 --> 00:38:34,625
♪ Narrate the story till morning ♪

672
00:38:34,625 --> 00:38:37,958
♪ Till the journey of life is over ♪

673
00:38:38,000 --> 00:38:40,625
♪ Narrate the story till morning ♪

674
00:38:40,666 --> 00:38:43,541
♪ Till the journey of life is over ♪

675
00:38:43,583 --> 00:38:46,041
♪ Is it a story or a tale of grief? ♪

676
00:38:46,041 --> 00:38:49,791
♪ It's truly a sad thing ♪

677
00:38:56,041 --> 00:38:57,375
[FIREWORKS]

678
00:38:58,666 --> 00:38:59,666
Whatʼs that?

679
00:38:59,833 --> 00:39:01,041
Bhootha Kola has begun.

680
00:39:01,583 --> 00:39:03,458
Itʼs an annual ritual
that is celebrated.

681
00:39:07,166 --> 00:39:08,166
Take out the vehicle.

682
00:39:08,750 --> 00:39:11,208
I heard the forest officer was
acting too smart the other day.

683
00:39:11,625 --> 00:39:13,416
Had I been there,
Iʼd have slapped him!

684
00:39:13,458 --> 00:39:15,208
You seem like an angry
man, aren't you?

685
00:39:15,208 --> 00:39:18,458
When I get angry,
I canʼt tolerate injustice.

686
00:39:18,708 --> 00:39:20,666
My body begins to...

687
00:39:24,500 --> 00:39:26,208
What? Empty already?
- Yep.

688
00:39:26,208 --> 00:39:27,500
Dammit! We should've got more.

689
00:39:27,541 --> 00:39:30,250
Shivanna,
can you return my bike key?

690
00:39:30,250 --> 00:39:31,291
Why?

691
00:39:31,291 --> 00:39:32,625
Sister Leela is here.

692
00:39:32,666 --> 00:39:34,125
She'll teach me
to ride the bike.

693
00:39:34,125 --> 00:39:36,250
When did she come?
- Did she finish her training?

694
00:39:36,250 --> 00:39:38,833
Yep. If she gets the job,
she will earn 1000 bucks a month.

695
00:39:38,833 --> 00:39:41,583
What? Really?
- 1000 bucks?!

696
00:39:42,291 --> 00:39:43,791
Give me a minute. Iʼll be back.

697
00:39:43,833 --> 00:39:45,458
Did he fall in love
with her salary?

698
00:39:49,250 --> 00:39:50,750
Thousand bucks in
a month is great.

699
00:39:50,791 --> 00:39:52,000
Shiva!
- Yes?

700
00:39:52,041 --> 00:39:53,166
Come here.

701
00:39:54,708 --> 00:39:55,708
What?

702
00:39:56,625 --> 00:39:58,041
Donʼt drink too much.

703
00:39:58,250 --> 00:40:00,708
No mom. I wonʼt drink today.

704
00:40:00,750 --> 00:40:03,000
Iʼll watch the whole performance.
- Let me see.

705
00:40:03,041 --> 00:40:04,958
Ideally, you should
be the one performing Kola.

706
00:40:05,000 --> 00:40:06,458
But youʼre so irresponsible.

707
00:40:06,458 --> 00:40:08,000
Thank god! Leave me alone!

708
00:40:08,000 --> 00:40:10,125
I have no plans to vanish
like her husband did.

709
00:40:10,166 --> 00:40:12,375
I want to enjoy life.
- You and your enjoyment.

710
00:40:13,916 --> 00:40:15,250
The Landlord is here.

711
00:40:15,708 --> 00:40:16,708
I'm coming.

712
00:40:16,750 --> 00:40:18,583
This is Girijakka.
- Greetings!

713
00:40:18,583 --> 00:40:19,750
Hope you're doing well.

714
00:40:20,083 --> 00:40:21,583
Take this.
Alright.

715
00:40:22,666 --> 00:40:23,791
God bless everyone.

716
00:40:28,916 --> 00:40:29,958
Shiva!

717
00:40:30,083 --> 00:40:31,291
You look pretty suave, eh?!

718
00:40:34,708 --> 00:40:35,708
Oy! Stop!

719
00:40:48,208 --> 00:40:49,333
Hey Shiva!

720
00:40:49,375 --> 00:40:50,916
Looks like you didnʼt see me!

721
00:40:50,916 --> 00:40:52,125
Attention devotees!

722
00:40:52,583 --> 00:40:56,250
Food offerings are being served.
Kindly go to the dining area.

723
00:40:57,833 --> 00:40:59,208
Where did she go?

724
00:41:06,458 --> 00:41:07,833
Move it! Iʼll serve this line.

725
00:41:10,000 --> 00:41:12,625
Salad! Ivy Gourd.

726
00:41:13,291 --> 00:41:14,500
Salad!

727
00:41:14,958 --> 00:41:17,208
Shivanna! Leela's here.
Her training is over.

728
00:41:17,250 --> 00:41:18,958
She will stay here.
- Is that so?

729
00:41:18,958 --> 00:41:20,833
Nice!
- Pass the fritters.

730
00:41:21,791 --> 00:41:24,208
Shivanna, thatʼs enough.
Others have to eat, too.

731
00:41:24,208 --> 00:41:25,291
It's okay. Enjoy.

732
00:41:25,291 --> 00:41:27,375
He's always been like that.
He is very fond of me.

733
00:41:27,916 --> 00:41:29,291
Ivy Gourd salad.

734
00:41:30,625 --> 00:41:31,625
Salad.

735
00:41:36,333 --> 00:41:37,375
Acting cocky, huh?

736
00:41:38,416 --> 00:41:39,416
Donʼt you remember me?

737
00:41:41,625 --> 00:41:43,375
You might have
completed your training.

