978
00:54:46,625 --> 00:54:48,958
Iʼm glad you didnʼt get wet!
Come now!

979
00:54:48,958 --> 00:54:49,958
What the heck!

980
00:55:01,083 --> 00:55:02,291
Heʼs back again!

981
00:55:02,291 --> 00:55:04,625
This guy has taken
us for granted.

982
00:55:04,916 --> 00:55:06,458
Where are you going?
- Iʼll be back.

983
00:55:06,500 --> 00:55:08,166
Sundar,
donʼt get into a fist fight.

984
00:55:08,291 --> 00:55:09,666
Officer, whatʼs the matter now?

985
00:55:09,666 --> 00:55:10,708
Encroachment.

986
00:55:11,666 --> 00:55:12,666
What is it?

987
00:55:12,708 --> 00:55:13,875
Attachment it seems.

988
00:55:14,041 --> 00:55:15,041
Attachment?

989
00:55:15,250 --> 00:55:17,458
Greetings, sir.
The labourers are here.

990
00:55:17,458 --> 00:55:18,458
Okay.

991
00:55:20,208 --> 00:55:23,458
How come I don’t see
the usual sour faces?

992
00:55:25,583 --> 00:55:26,583
Come here.

993
00:55:28,625 --> 00:55:29,625
Just come!

994
00:55:30,333 --> 00:55:31,375
Speak.

995
00:55:31,375 --> 00:55:32,708
They're your
people, aren't they?

996
00:55:32,708 --> 00:55:34,333
They would rather
listen to you than me.

997
00:55:34,375 --> 00:55:35,750
Leela, whatʼs the matter?

998
00:55:38,833 --> 00:55:39,916
Go stand at the back.

999
00:55:39,916 --> 00:55:42,125
This is the result when you
use influence to get a job.

1000
00:55:43,916 --> 00:55:45,208
This is a government order.

1001
00:55:45,250 --> 00:55:47,708
The department has to measure
the circumference of the forest.

1002
00:55:47,916 --> 00:55:50,625
We will have to report
the encroachment.

1003
00:55:50,750 --> 00:55:52,041
Am I clear?

1004
00:55:54,083 --> 00:55:56,291
Sir, where is the survey stone?

1005
00:55:56,625 --> 00:55:58,750
Follow the officer.

1006
00:55:59,166 --> 00:56:00,166
Go there.

1007
00:56:00,208 --> 00:56:01,500
Start surveying from that stone.

1008
00:56:01,916 --> 00:56:04,083
Make way! Let them work.

1009
00:56:04,083 --> 00:56:05,458
Drag the chain to that stone.

1010
00:56:05,458 --> 00:56:06,750
Bring the chain this side.

1011
00:56:06,791 --> 00:56:09,208
What attachment are
you talking about?

1012
00:56:09,250 --> 00:56:10,833
Itʼs not attachment.
Itʼs encroachment.

1013
00:56:10,833 --> 00:56:12,708
I got that. What does it mean?

1014
00:56:12,708 --> 00:56:13,916
Whatʼs your name?

1015
00:56:13,958 --> 00:56:15,291
Attachment.
I mean.. Sundar.

1016
00:56:16,375 --> 00:56:18,708
Sundar, encroachment means
illegally occupied land.

1017
00:56:18,708 --> 00:56:20,041
Issue a notice to the concerned.

1018
00:56:20,041 --> 00:56:21,041
Go fast!

1019
00:56:21,208 --> 00:56:23,500
You were supposed to reply to the notice.
But you havenʼt.

1020
00:56:23,541 --> 00:56:26,416
We were busy! What now?

1021
00:56:27,041 --> 00:56:29,541
I know. Thatʼs why we are here.

1022
00:56:30,208 --> 00:56:31,708
We are peaceful people.

1023
00:56:32,041 --> 00:56:34,291
Just don't provoke us.

1024
00:56:34,333 --> 00:56:37,291
If we claim your land,
will you be okay with it?

1025
00:56:37,333 --> 00:56:38,458
You have done that already.

1026
00:56:38,791 --> 00:56:40,208
You've fenced our land.

1027
00:56:40,708 --> 00:56:42,666
Itʼs a one hour job.

1028
00:56:42,958 --> 00:56:46,291
We will shift the stones which your ancestors
and you have been moving since years.

1029
00:56:46,291 --> 00:56:48,791
This will not happen
as long as Iʼm alive!

1030
00:56:48,833 --> 00:56:50,458
Hey Sundar. Hold on.
Try stopping us.

1031
00:56:50,458 --> 00:56:51,916
Ay! Go back.

1032
00:56:51,958 --> 00:56:53,833
Once I take a step
forward, I won't step back.

1033
00:56:53,833 --> 00:56:55,750
On the night of Kola,
I was held back.

1034
00:56:55,750 --> 00:56:57,250
Are you showing off?

1035
00:56:57,958 --> 00:56:59,583
You donʼt have to pull
your gun for that.

1036
00:56:59,625 --> 00:57:02,291
I have a gun too.
It'll take time for me to bring it.

1037
00:57:03,166 --> 00:57:04,708
I said get back!!

1038
00:57:04,750 --> 00:57:06,041
Donʼt touch us!

1039
00:57:06,083 --> 00:57:07,291
Youʼre acting too smart.

1040
00:57:07,291 --> 00:57:08,541
I can fight too!

1041
00:57:08,583 --> 00:57:09,625
Go back, I said!

1042
00:57:12,708 --> 00:57:13,708
Where's Shiva?

1043
00:57:16,458 --> 00:57:19,125
Shivanna!
The forest officer is troubling us!

1044
00:57:20,125 --> 00:57:21,708
Leela, what are you doing dear?

1045
00:57:21,708 --> 00:57:23,708
You've joined them to
fence your own land?

1046
00:57:23,750 --> 00:57:25,333
Please let me do my job dad.

1047
00:57:25,458 --> 00:57:27,291
We don't need this
insensitive job.

1048
00:57:28,291 --> 00:57:30,708
Shut up people!

1049
00:57:30,750 --> 00:57:32,083
Go on, speak.

1050
00:57:32,416 --> 00:57:34,041
You guys just donʼt
respect my words.

1051
00:57:34,583 --> 00:57:35,875
Go on!
- Now listen.

1052
00:57:36,500 --> 00:57:38,333
Even I donʼt know
whatʼs happening.

1053
00:57:38,333 --> 00:57:40,500
Then why the hell
are you talking?!

1054
00:57:40,500 --> 00:57:42,250
I mean I donʼt know the
procedures involved.

1055
00:57:42,291 --> 00:57:43,750
Why are you pouncing
on me for that?!

1056
00:57:44,083 --> 00:57:47,000
After all,
he also has to perform his duty.

1057
00:57:47,000 --> 00:57:48,958
He'll be under pressure too.
- For what?!

1058
00:57:48,958 --> 00:57:50,708
Voting for you was
our biggest mistake.

1059
00:57:50,708 --> 00:57:52,125
Now youʼre also on his side!

1060
00:57:52,125 --> 00:57:54,708
No way!
Only the labourers were mine.

1061
00:57:54,750 --> 00:57:56,666
Iʼm on your side!
- Enough. We donʼt believe you.

1062
00:57:56,666 --> 00:57:58,583
We know what to do.
Come letʼs go.

1063
00:57:58,625 --> 00:57:59,708
Please listen to me!

1064
00:57:59,708 --> 00:58:01,250
Don't my words have
any value at all?

1065
00:58:01,250 --> 00:58:02,291
Hey, get lost!

1066
00:58:02,333 --> 00:58:04,958
Wait!
Donʼt disturb while marking.

1067
00:58:08,875 --> 00:58:10,583
Who are you to mark our land?

1068
00:58:16,916 --> 00:58:18,333
Thrash him right!

1069
00:58:22,583 --> 00:58:23,583
Sir!

1070
00:58:25,291 --> 00:58:26,291
Police!

1071
00:59:07,541 --> 00:59:09,166
Rabid dog!

1072
00:59:19,166 --> 00:59:20,208
Come to me! You jackas*!

1073
00:59:47,958 --> 00:59:50,583
I will finish you today, Bas*ard!

1074
00:59:55,166 --> 00:59:56,166
[GUNSHOT]

1075
01:00:00,750 --> 01:00:02,791
What's the big deal
about firing in the air?!

1076
01:00:02,791 --> 01:00:04,916
Shoot me directly if
you have the guts!

1077
01:00:04,958 --> 01:00:06,000
Shoot!

1078
01:00:06,458 --> 01:00:07,458
[GUNSHOT]

1079
01:00:10,833 --> 01:00:12,208
I didnʼt miss my aim.

1080
01:00:12,791 --> 01:00:14,166
I'm a trained officer.

1081
01:00:15,791 --> 01:00:16,791
Tie him up.

1082
01:00:37,833 --> 01:00:39,875
You have done the right
thing, sir.

1083
01:00:40,291 --> 01:00:42,291
Go inside!
Iʼll kick you all behind bars.

1084
01:00:53,541 --> 01:00:54,541
Take care.

1085
01:01:03,791 --> 01:01:06,333
Youʼre still wearing that
uniform, girl?

1086
01:01:06,333 --> 01:01:08,166
We thought you'll get
educated and help us.

1087
01:01:08,208 --> 01:01:09,666
But you back stabbed us.

1088
01:01:18,291 --> 01:01:20,000
Heʼs not eaten
anything since morning.

1089
01:01:34,708 --> 01:01:35,708
Shiva!

1090
01:01:38,166 --> 01:01:40,125
I heard you didn't
eat since morning.

1091
01:01:47,625 --> 01:01:48,666
Get lost!

1092
01:01:48,666 --> 01:01:49,750
Leela!

1093
01:01:49,750 --> 01:01:51,958
How dare you beat up a girl!

1094
01:01:52,333 --> 01:01:55,291
This was the last thing
I expected from you!

1095
01:01:55,291 --> 01:01:56,666
Where are you going?! Stop!

1096
01:02:01,583 --> 01:02:05,583
How would I know that they would ask
me to do this on the first day at work?!

1097
01:02:06,791 --> 01:02:09,708
None of you understand
my situation!

1098
01:02:19,083 --> 01:02:20,083
Annappa.

1099
01:02:22,333 --> 01:02:25,375
If you submit a request for the title
deed, things will move fast.

1100
01:02:25,416 --> 01:02:26,416
Illiterates!

1101
01:02:26,458 --> 01:02:27,458
Naru.

1102
01:02:27,500 --> 01:02:29,250
Naru, be quick.

1103
01:02:29,958 --> 01:02:31,875
None of your
documents are in place.

1104
01:02:31,875 --> 01:02:33,625
Itʼs been a while,
must have gathered dust.

1105
01:02:33,625 --> 01:02:36,291
Screw the dust!
I can't read a single letter.

1106
01:02:36,333 --> 01:02:37,333
Damn.

1107
01:02:38,250 --> 01:02:39,250
Who is Thukra?

1108
01:02:40,541 --> 01:02:42,083
Itʼs my father.
- What?

1109
01:02:42,583 --> 01:02:44,041
Whose document is this?
Itʼs mine.

1110
01:02:44,375 --> 01:02:46,875
How did his documents get
registered in your father’s name?

1111
01:02:46,875 --> 01:02:48,833
Both our fathers have
the same name - Thukra.

1112
01:02:49,916 --> 01:02:52,291
These Thukras are trouble!

1113
01:02:52,333 --> 01:02:53,333
Apply your thumb imprint.

1114
01:02:53,541 --> 01:02:55,583
Whose ration card is this?
- Itʼs mine! Abu.

1115
01:02:56,041 --> 01:02:58,083
You think Iʼm selling
rice, here?

1116
01:02:59,208 --> 01:03:00,583
What the hell?!

1117
01:03:01,125 --> 01:03:02,541
Tell me if youʼre
not selling rice.

1118
01:03:02,583 --> 01:03:03,625
Why get angry for that?

1119
01:03:03,666 --> 01:03:05,041
What?
- The house is beautiful.

1120
01:03:05,041 --> 01:03:06,708
As if he's giving rice
from his own kitchen.

1121
01:03:06,750 --> 01:03:11,125
I want the documents in place or else
it will be tough to argue in court.

1122
01:03:12,458 --> 01:03:13,791
What is it?

1123
01:03:18,291 --> 01:03:20,458
How dare you step in?!
You mongrel!

1124
01:03:31,583 --> 01:03:33,458
Hey brother, stop!!
- Moron! Iʼll kill you!

1125
01:03:33,458 --> 01:03:34,458
Bulla, donʼt step in.

1126
01:03:36,666 --> 01:03:39,291
Mohan, go mind your business!

1127
01:03:44,125 --> 01:03:45,166
Shiva!
- Yes Landlord?

1128
01:03:45,208 --> 01:03:46,375
Nothing to worry.

1129
01:03:46,375 --> 01:03:47,958
He is always tension free!

1130
01:03:48,250 --> 01:03:49,291
This is for you. Enjoy.

1131
01:03:49,291 --> 01:03:50,291
Please have the drink.

1132
01:03:50,333 --> 01:03:51,375
Landlord, what about you?

1133
01:03:51,375 --> 01:03:52,916
Iʼll have. You please drink.
- Okay.

1134
01:03:52,916 --> 01:03:54,125
Please relax.
- Okay.

1135
01:03:56,333 --> 01:03:59,541
Don't chug insane amount of alcohol just
because it's free. Watch the intake!

1136
01:04:03,208 --> 01:04:07,125
He hit me in front of everyone but
this Landlord too supports him.

1137
01:04:07,500 --> 01:04:10,333
Exactly. Are you a rabid dog
to get treated like that?

1138
01:04:11,750 --> 01:04:12,750
Mohan.

1139
01:04:13,708 --> 01:04:15,291
Every dog has its day.

1140
01:04:16,625 --> 01:04:17,750
We shall bite then.

1141
01:04:22,291 --> 01:04:23,833
You please carry on.
Iʼll be back soon.

1142
01:04:23,875 --> 01:04:25,125
Sir, peanuts?

1143
01:04:29,375 --> 01:04:31,666
I hope our land will be safe.

1144
01:04:32,416 --> 01:04:34,291
Why are you requesting me?

1145
01:04:35,166 --> 01:04:37,833
You are like our
Landlord, Shivanna.

1146
01:04:45,750 --> 01:04:48,416
Where do you think my land is?
Itʼs right beside the forest.

1147
01:04:48,833 --> 01:04:52,208
They marked my land
as encroachment.

1148
01:04:52,250 --> 01:04:53,250
Then?

1149
01:04:53,291 --> 01:04:57,958
Then I realised I didnʼt
have the right documents.

1150
01:04:57,958 --> 01:04:58,958
Oh!

1151
01:04:59,500 --> 01:05:00,541
Now?

1152
01:05:00,583 --> 01:05:08,541
A lawyer called Subbarao is
fighting the case since 12 years.

1153
01:05:10,083 --> 01:05:11,208
Someday, I might win.

1154
01:05:11,250 --> 01:05:12,250
Shiva!

1155
01:05:12,458 --> 01:05:13,458
Yes, Landlord.

1156
01:05:13,458 --> 01:05:15,291
We need to water the plantation.
Shall we go?

1157
01:05:15,291 --> 01:05:16,458
Okay.

1158
01:05:21,833 --> 01:05:23,125
Be quick.
- Shiva, take this.

1159
01:05:25,208 --> 01:05:26,250
Take the flash light.

1160
01:05:26,291 --> 01:05:27,958
Careful.
- Okay Ammakka.

1161
01:05:28,208 --> 01:05:29,416
You think they realised?

1162
01:05:29,458 --> 01:05:30,916
They were all in a
buzz, Landlord.

1163
01:05:31,083 --> 01:05:33,125
Shiva, what happened
to that match of yours?

1164
01:05:33,375 --> 01:05:34,875
Seen her on your bike often.

1165
01:05:34,916 --> 01:05:36,041
What happened to it?

1166
01:05:36,458 --> 01:05:37,750
We were going strong.

1167
01:05:37,750 --> 01:05:40,166
Until this forest officer spoilt it for us.
We broke up.

1168
01:05:40,208 --> 01:05:42,125
Can you get her removed from the
job, Landlord?

1169
01:05:42,166 --> 01:05:43,666
What can the poor girl do?

1170
01:05:43,666 --> 01:05:45,458
She only followed
the DRFOʼs orders.

1171
01:05:45,500 --> 01:05:47,041
Can you get him
removed from his post?

1172
01:05:47,375 --> 01:05:49,500
Itʼs not so easy Shiva.

1173
01:05:50,333 --> 01:05:52,791
If heʼs not performing his
duty, then we can try.

1174
01:05:52,833 --> 01:05:53,916
Is it so?

1175
01:05:54,041 --> 01:05:56,083
Then letʼs ensure he
doesnʼt perform his duty.

1176
01:05:56,208 --> 01:05:57,958
Besides, we have you with us.

1177
01:05:58,791 --> 01:06:00,166
Youʼre a smart guy Shiva!

1178
01:06:00,500 --> 01:06:02,833
You get things instantly!

1179
01:06:07,375 --> 01:06:09,458
The signal's here.
- Careful, my lord.

1180
01:06:17,625 --> 01:06:18,666
Come fast lady.

1181
01:07:02,791 --> 01:07:03,875
What happened?

1182
01:07:03,875 --> 01:07:05,875
What happened, Shiva?
- I saw something there. Run!

1183
01:07:07,250 --> 01:07:09,166
What happened?
Tell me what is it.

1184
01:07:09,208 --> 01:07:11,083
Hold the torch you idiot!
I can't see anything.

1185
01:07:11,083 --> 01:07:14,000
Take this! You can return it
if we make it out of here alive!

1186
01:07:14,000 --> 01:07:15,958
I was in a hurry because
her husband would return.

1187
01:07:16,083 --> 01:07:17,583
Shiva!
I'm going! You go home too!

1188
01:07:17,583 --> 01:07:19,375
Shiva! Stop!

1189
01:07:34,250 --> 01:07:36,666
When will you realise not to
roam the forest at such hours?

1190
01:07:36,666 --> 01:07:39,166
This is what you get for getting
into worthless adventures.

1191
01:07:39,416 --> 01:07:40,750
Don't get started.

1192
01:07:40,750 --> 01:07:41,958
Let him recover.

1193
01:07:44,875 --> 01:07:46,750
I’m advising because
you’re younger to me.

1194
01:07:46,750 --> 01:07:49,625
At your age, your father would visit
couple of villages to perform Kola.

1195
01:07:49,666 --> 01:07:51,250
Why don't you get it?

1196
01:07:51,250 --> 01:07:52,291
Why will he get it?

1197
01:07:52,333 --> 01:07:55,375
If he's busy with these wastrels,
how will he have time for anything else?

1198
01:07:55,416 --> 01:07:57,750
Why blame us for nothing?
Did we blind him?

1199
01:07:57,916 --> 01:07:59,333
I'll punch you. Shut up!

1200
01:07:59,583 --> 01:08:01,375
Why keep blaming
us for everything?

1201
01:08:01,541 --> 01:08:02,666
Let's get out.

1202
01:08:03,708 --> 01:08:05,125
We'll wait outside. Take care.

1203
01:08:06,291 --> 01:08:08,000
If you have something to
say, tell it to me.

1204
01:08:08,041 --> 01:08:09,166
Why blame others?

1205
01:08:09,708 --> 01:08:11,083
You sure get angry
for everything.

1206
01:08:11,125 --> 01:08:14,083
Enough now.
Let's not blow it out of proportion.

1207
01:08:17,791 --> 01:08:20,666
Brother, pray to the
Demigod before leaving.

1208
01:08:20,916 --> 01:08:22,500
Good things will come your way.
- Okay.

1209
01:08:26,250 --> 01:08:28,333
Alas! here comes the forest officer.

1210
01:08:28,333 --> 01:08:29,416
Bloody scoundrel!

1211
01:08:30,083 --> 01:08:32,625
Filling up the trenches marked,
doesn't make the forest theirs.

1212
01:08:32,625 --> 01:08:33,916
Let us wait and watch.

1213
01:08:39,166 --> 01:08:40,208
Boom!

1214
01:08:41,458 --> 01:08:42,583
Working fine, right?

1215
01:08:43,333 --> 01:08:45,166
Rampa get your gun repaired.

1216
01:08:45,208 --> 01:08:46,916
Itʼs training time.

1217
01:08:47,833 --> 01:08:49,541
Unlike others,
I don't miss my targets.

1218
01:08:50,958 --> 01:08:51,958
Carry on.

1219
01:09:15,416 --> 01:09:18,708
♪ The Siruras nature
is all around ♪

1220
01:09:18,916 --> 01:09:22,583
♪ The peacock we saw
has spread its feathers ♪

1221
01:09:29,625 --> 01:09:32,708
♪ In Bulpadi's lake, a boat arrived. ♪

1222
01:09:33,208 --> 01:09:36,250
♪ Upon which a fish had hopped. ♪

